sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_matsa_quick_serv.quick_service_formatter_utils</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>quick_service_formatter_utils</name><script><![CDATA[var quick_service_formatter_utils = Class.create();
quick_service_formatter_utils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	
	attachmentsDisabled: function() {
		return gs.getProperty('x_matsa_quick_serv.disableAllAttachments');
	},
	
	
	getList: function() {
		var todos = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_variables');
		//todos.addQuery('opened_by', gs.getUserID());
		todos.orderBy('opened_at');
		todos.query();
		
		var list = [];
		while (todos.next()) {
			list.push(todos.variable.question_text + '');
		}
		
		gs.addInfoMessage(list.toString());
		return list.toString();
		//return new global.JSON().encodeArray(list);
	},
	
	getVars: function(sysID){
		if(this.getParameter('sysparm_current_sysId'))
			sysID = this.getParameter('sysparm_current_sysId');
		var theseVars = false;
		var varObj = {};
		var current = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task');
		current.get(sysID);
		var varRelationships = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_variable_lists');
		varRelationships.addEncodedQuery('variable.active=true^catalog_item='+current.request_item.cat_item.sys_id.toString());
		varRelationships.query();
		while (varRelationships.next()){
		//gs.info("getVars: "+varRelationships.variable.question_text.toString());
			
			varObj[varRelationships.getUniqueValue()] = {
				"variable_sysID":varRelationships.variable.sys_id.toString(),
				"label":varRelationships.variable.question_text.toString(),
				"name":varRelationships.variable.name.toString(),
				"display_value":'',
				"value":''
			};
		}
		
		var gr = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
		if (gr.get(current.request_item.toString())) {
			for (var index in varObj){
				if(typeof(gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID]) !== 'undefined'){
					varObj[index].display_value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID].getDisplayValue();
					varObj[index].value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID.toString()].toString();
				}
				
			}
		}
		theseVars = global.JSON.stringify(varObj);
		gs.info("getVars: "+theseVars);
		return theseVars;
	},
	
	type: 'quick_service_formatter_utils'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>cloudpires</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-06-22 12:06:37</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>2e54f041dba73200e46473abbf9619d7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>quick_service_formatter_utils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_2e54f041dba73200e46473abbf9619d7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-08-14 19:18:29</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><name>QS - Process Inbound Task Insert</name><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period>1970-01-01 00:00:05</run_period><run_start>2018-08-14 15:00:50</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 05:00:00</run_time><run_type>periodically</run_type><script><![CDATA[var inbnd_tsk_ins = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound');
inbnd_tsk_ins.addEncodedQuery("task_type=qs task^action=insert^status=ready"+
						   "^NQtask_type=qs task^action=insert^status=error^retry_count<6");
inbnd_tsk_ins.orderBy('sys_created_on');
inbnd_tsk_ins.query();
while (inbnd_tsk_ins.next()) {
 if (inbnd_tsk_ins.status == 'ready'||inbnd_tsk_ins.status == 'error')
	 quick_service_utils.inbound_task_insert(inbnd_tsk_ins);
	 
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-14 15:01:08</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>d82582a7dbff93002e2f28f3ca961980</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process Inbound Task Insert</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_d82582a7dbff93002e2f28f3ca961980</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-09 12:21:04</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>QS - Sync QS Task</name><order>500</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	//gs.info("in the sync qs task business rule");
	// 	if(quick_service_utils.qsTaskUpdated(current, previous))
	// 		quick_service_utils.syncTask();
	
	
		//if(quick_service_utils.qsTaskUpdated(current, previous)){
			if(current.operation()=="update" && current.sys_updated_by!='6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441'){
				var flag=0;
				var inbound =new GlideRecord("x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound");

				inbound.addQuery("action","insert");
				//inbound.addEncodedQuery("server_request="+current.request.sys_id.toString()+"^action=insert");
				inbound.query();
				while(inbound.next()){
					flag=1;
					var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
					gr.initialize();
					gr.local_task=current.sys_id;
					gr.server_request = current.request;
					gr.type = 'outbound';
					gr.task_type = 'qs task';
					gr.task_parameters = current.quick_service_customer_comments;
					gr.action = 'update';
					gr.status = 'ready';
					gr.client_task = inbound.client_task;
					gr.customer = inbound.customer;
					gr.insert();
					break;
				}
				if(flag==0)
				{
				//	gs.addInfoMessage("flag is zero");
				var outbound =new GlideRecord("x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound");
				outbound.addQuery("local_task",current.sys_id);
				outbound.addQuery("action","insert");
				outbound.query();
				while(outbound.next()){
					//gs.addInfoMessage("this task is inserted by this instance");
					var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
					gr.initialize();
					gr.local_task=current.sys_id;
					gr.server_request = current.request;
					gr.type = 'outbound';
					gr.task_type = 'qs task';
					gr.task_parameters = current.quick_service_customer_comments;
					gr.action = 'update';
					gr.status = 'ready';
					var payloadObj=JSON.parse(outbound.payload);
					//gs.addInfoMessage(payloadObj.client_task);
					gr.client_task = payloadObj.u_client_task;
					//gr.client_task = outbound.client_task;
					gr.customer = outbound.customer;
					gr.insert();
					break;
				}		
			}
			}else if(current.operation()=="insert" && current.opened_by!="6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441"){
				var flag=0;
				
				var inbound =new GlideRecord("x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound");
				inbound.addQuery("server_request",current.request);
				inbound.addQuery("action","insert");
				inbound.query();
				while(inbound.next()){
					flag=1;
					//gs.info("this is logged from demo6");
				}
				if(flag==0){
					quick_service_utils.syncTask();
				}
				
			}
			
			
			
			
			
			
		
		
	})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>cloudpires</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-06-21 11:46:11</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>67a56360db633200e46473abbf96195b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>53</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Sync QS Task</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_67a56360db633200e46473abbf96195b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-10 18:44:58</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=67a56360db633200e46473abbf96195b"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>false</active><api_name>x_matsa_quick_serv.quick_service_utils</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>This is the old one</description><name>quick_service_utils</name><script><![CDATA[var quick_service_utils = Class.create();
quick_service_utils.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    type: 'quick_service_utils'
};

quick_service_utils.setTaskValuesOnLoad = function() {
    current.request_item = current.parent.sys_id.toString();
};

quick_service_utils.getVariableSets = function(catItem) {

    var ids = [];

    var gr = new GlideRecord('io_set_item');
    gr.addEncodedQuery('sc_cat_item=' + catItem);
    gr.query();
    while (gr.next()) {

        var varSet = new GlideRecord('item_option_new');
        varSet.addEncodedQuery('variable_set=' + gr.variable_set.sys_id);
        varSet.query();
        while (varSet.next()) {

            ids.push(new String(varSet.sys_id));
        }
    }
    var newVars = new GlideRecord('item_option_new');
    newVars.addEncodedQuery('cat_item=' + catItem);
    newVars.query();
    while (newVars.next()) {
        ids.push(new String(newVars.sys_id));
    }

    var qsVars = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_variables');
    qsVars.addEncodedQuery('catalog_item=' + catItem + '^variable!=NULL');
    qsVars.query();
    while (qsVars.next()) {

        var arrayUtil = new global.ArrayUtil();
        var index = arrayUtil.indexOf(ids, qsVars.variable.sys_id);
        if (index > -1)
            ids.splice(index, 1);

    }

    return ids;
};

quick_service_utils.quickServiceActive = function (){
    var active = false;
    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    if (quickServiceConfig.get('active', true))
        active = true;
    return active;
};

quick_service_utils.relationshipActive = function(sysID, action) {
    var relationshipActive = false;
    var relationship = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
    relationship.addQuery('local_record', sysID);
    relationship.addQuery('active', 'true');
    relationship.query();

    if (relationship.next()) {
        relationshipActive = true;
        if (action == 'deactivate') {
            relationship.active = false;
            relationship.update();
            relationshipActive = 'deactivated';
        }
    }
    return relationshipActive;
};

quick_service_utils.incidentUpdated = function(current, previous) {

    var fieldArr = quick_service_utils.getFields();
    var fieldsUpdated = false;

    for (var index in fieldArr) {
        if (current[fieldArr[index]] != previous[fieldArr[index]].toString()) {
            fieldsUpdated = true;
        }
    }
    return fieldsUpdated;

};

quick_service_utils.getFields = function() {

    var fieldsToMap = ['state'];

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);

    var incidentFields = new GlideRecord('sys_dictionary');
    incidentFields.addEncodedQuery("sys_idIN" + quickServiceConfig.qs_incidents_fields);
    incidentFields.query();
    while (incidentFields.next()) {
        if(fieldsToMap.indexOf(incidentFields.element.toString())<0)
            fieldsToMap.push(incidentFields.element.toString());
    }
    return fieldsToMap;
};

quick_service_utils.qsTaskUpdated = function(current, previous) {

    var fieldArr = quick_service_utils.getQsTaskFields(current.sys_id);
    var fieldsUpdated = false;
    for (var index in fieldArr) {

        if ((typeof(current[fieldArr[index]]) !== 'undefined') && (current[fieldArr[index]] != previous[fieldArr[index]])) {
            fieldsUpdated = true;
        }
    }
    return fieldsUpdated;

};

quick_service_utils.getQsTaskFields = function(sysID) {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var fieldsToMap = ["state","assigned_to","assignment_group","quick_service_customer_comments"];
    //fieldsToMap.push(quickServiceConfig)

    return fieldsToMap;
};

quick_service_utils.incidentResolved = function(incident_state) {
    var resolved = false;
    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var resolutionStates = quickServiceConfig.incident_resolved_state.getDisplayValue().split(',');

    for (var index in resolutionStates) {
        if (incident_state == resolutionStates[index].trim()) {
            resolved = true;
        }
    }
    return resolved;
};

quick_service_utils.syncTask = function(override, parameters) {
    // Create Outbound request

    if(quick_service_utils.quickServiceActive()){
        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
        gr.initialize();
        gr.type = 'outbound';
        gr.action = current.operation();
        if (override == 'insert')
            gr.action = override;
        gr.status = 'ready';
        gr.local_task = current.getUniqueValue();
        gr.customer = 'the customer';
        if (override == "qsIncidentCreate") {
            gr.task_type = "incident";
            gr.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(current); //parameters;

        } else if (current.sys_class_name.toString() == "x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task") {
            gr.task_type = "qs task";
            gr.task_parameters = current.quick_service_customer_comments;

        } else if (current.sys_class_name.toString() == "incident") {
            gr.task_type = "incident";
            gr.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(current);

        }
        gr.insert();
    } else {
        gs.addErrorMessage('QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord')
        gs.info("QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord")
    }
    return;

};

quick_service_utils.outbound_request = function() {
    if(quick_service_utils.quickServiceActive()){
        if (current.status == 'ready') {
            var additionalValues;

            if (current.action == 'insert') {

                if (this.outbound_insert()) {
                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_insert();
                } else {
                    return;
                }
            } else if (current.action == 'update') {

                if (this.outbound_update()) {
                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_update();
                } else {
                    return;
                }
            } else if (current.action == 'delete_attachment' || current.action == 'add_attachment') {

                if (this.outbound_update()) {
                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_update();
                } else {
                    return;
                }
            }

            try {
                var user = current.quick_service_host.user_name;
                var password = current.quick_service_host.password.getDecryptedValue();

                var quick_service_task_obj = {
                    "number": current.local_task.number.toString(),
                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
                };
                var payloadObj = {};
                payloadObj.u_payload = additionalValues.toString();
                payloadObj.u_action = current.action.toString();
                payloadObj.u_customer = current.quick_service_host.server_config_record.toString();
                payloadObj.u_client_task = JSON.stringify(quick_service_task_obj);
                try {
                    payloadObj.u_server_task = current.local_task.qs_task_sysid.toString();
                } catch (err) {}
                payloadObj.u_task_type = current.task_type.toString();
                var payloadString = JSON.stringify(payloadObj);

                var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
                request.setEndpoint('https://' + current.quick_service_host.quick_service_host + '/api/now/table/u_qs_inbound');
                request.setHttpMethod('POST');
                request.setBasicAuth(user, password);
                request.setRequestHeader("Accept", "application/json");
                request.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
                request.setRequestBody(payloadString);

                var response = request.execute();
                var respBody = response.getBody();
                current.payload = payloadString;
                current.result = respBody;
                if (respBody.match(/^\{\"error\"/)) {
                    current.error = respBody;
                    current.status = 'error';
                } else {
                    current.status = 'processed';
                }
            } catch (err) {
                
                current.error = 'Error sending Webservice: ' + err;
                current.status = 'error';
            }

        if (current.status == 'error') {
            this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "outbound_request", current.local_task.toString(), current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
        }
            current.update();
        }
    } else {
        gs.info("QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord")
    }
};

quick_service_utils.outbound_insert = function() {
    var theseVars = false;
    if (current.task_type == 'qs task') {
        var varObj = {};
        try {
            var varRelationships = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_variables');
            varRelationships.addEncodedQuery('variable.active=true^catalog_item=' + current.local_task.request_item.cat_item.sys_id.toString());
            varRelationships.query();
            while (varRelationships.next()) {
                varObj[varRelationships.getUniqueValue()] = {
                    "variable_sysID": varRelationships.variable.sys_id.toString(),
                    "label": varRelationships.variable.question_text.toString(),
                    "name": varRelationships.variable.name.toString(),
                    "order": varRelationships.variable.order.toString(),
                    "display_value": '',
                    "value": ''
                };
            }

            var gr = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
            if (gr.get(current.local_task.request_item.toString())) {
                for (var index in varObj) {
                    try{
                        varObj[index].display_value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID].getDisplayValue();
                        varObj[index].value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID.toString()].toString();
                    }catch(err){
                        varObj[index].display_value = '';
                        varObj[index].value = '';
                        current.error += 'Field \"'+varObj[index].name+'\" error fetching vars: '+ err+ '\n';
                    }
                }
            }
            theseVars = global.JSON.stringify(varObj);
        } catch (err) {
            current.error = 'Error fetching vars: ' + err;
            current.status = 'error';
            current.update();
        }
    } else if (current.task_type == 'incident') {
        theseVars = current.task_parameters;
        theseVars.state= current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.number= current.local_task.number.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.assigned_to= current.local_task.assigned_to.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.assignment_group= current.local_task.assignment_group.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.qs_task= current.qs_task_number;
        theseVars.resolved= quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
        theseVars.active= !quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
    }
    return theseVars;
};

quick_service_utils.inbound_qsTask = function() {
    var varCount = 0;
    var localTask = current.local_task;
    var server_qs_task = global.JSON.parse(current.payload);
    try {
        var qs_task = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task');
        if (qs_task.get(current.local_task.toString())) {

            qs_task.qs_state = server_qs_task.state;
            if (server_qs_task.state.match(/Closed Complete/)) { // && qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.resolution_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.resolution_state.value;
            } else if (server_qs_task.state.match(/Closed/)) { // && qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.cancelled_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.cancelled_state.value;
            } else if (qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.open_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.open_state.value;
                if (!qs_task.active) {
                    qs_task.active = true;
                }
            }
            qs_task.qs_task_number = server_qs_task.number;
            qs_task.qs_assigned_to = server_qs_task.assigned_to;
            qs_task.qs_assignment_group = server_qs_task.assignment_group;
            qs_task.qs_task_sysid = server_qs_task.sys_id;
            qs_task.expedited_request = server_qs_task.u_expedited_request;
            qs_task.quickservice_closed_by = server_qs_task.closed_by;
            qs_task.close_notes = server_qs_task.close_notes;
            if (server_qs_task.work_notes && !server_qs_task.work_notes.match(/\_123STREAMENTRY321\_/g)) {
                var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
                quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
                qs_task[quickServiceConfig.qs_comments_field.element] = server_qs_task.updated_by + ' commented: ' + server_qs_task.work_notes;
            }
            qs_task.update();

            current.result = 'Task updated:' + qs_task.number;
            current.status = 'processed';
        } else {
            current.error = 'GlideRecord query returned no task';
            current.status = 'error';
        }
    } catch (err) {
        current.error = 'GlideRecord query failure: ' + err;
        current.status = 'error';
    }

    if (current.status == 'error') {
        this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "inbound_qsTask", localTask.sys_id, current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
    }
    current.update();
};

quick_service_utils.inbound_incident = function() {
    var retryCount = current.retry_count;
    var processing_results = 'Processing Results';
    var updated = false;
    var varCount = 0;
    var localTask = current.local_task;
    var newVars = global.JSON.parse(current.payload);
    try {
        var qs_relRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
        qs_relRec.addQuery('active', true);
        qs_relRec.addQuery('local_record', current.local_task);
        qs_relRec.query();
        if (qs_relRec.next()) {
            var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
            quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
            qs_relRec.quick_service_record = newVars.defaultFields.number;
            qs_relRec.client_task_data = '{"number":"' + newVars.defaultFields.number + '","sys_Id":' + newVars.defaultFields.sys_id + '"}';
            // Check if resolved
            if (newVars.defaultFields.resolved && quickServiceConfig.server_can_resolve) {
                qs_relRec.active = false;
            }

            var qs_notes = "Quick Service Notes\n";
            for (var field in newVars.fieldsToMap) {

                if ((typeof(qs_relRec[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]]) !== 'undefined') && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue) {
                    qs_relRec[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]] = newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                }
                if (newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].type == 'journal_input' && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue && !newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.match(/\_123STREAMENTRY321\_/g)) {
                        qs_notes = newVars.defaultFields.updated_by.toString() + " commented: " + newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                }
                updated = true;
            }
            // Check for work notes

            var modifiedFields = "";
            if (qs_relRec.all_fields) {
                var oldVars = JSON.parse(qs_relRec.all_fields);
                var fieldsModified = false;
                for (var index in newVars.customFields) {
                    if (newVars.customFields[index].value.toString() != oldVars[index].value.toString() && newVars.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input") {
                        if (!fieldsModified) {
                            modifiedFields = "\nModified Fields:\n";
                            fieldsModified = true;
                        }
                        modifiedFields += newVars.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + newVars.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
                    }
                }
            } else {
                for (var index in newVars.customFields) {
                    if (newVars.customFields[index].value && newVars.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input") {
                        if (!fieldsModified) {
                            modifiedFields = "\nModified Fields:\n";
                            fieldsModified = true;
                        }
                        modifiedFields += newVars.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + newVars.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
                    }
                }
            }

            qs_relRec.work_notes = qs_notes + modifiedFields;

            qs_relRec.all_fields = JSON.stringify(newVars.customFields);


            current.status = 'processed';
            try {
                var incidentUpdate = this.updateIncident(qs_relRec.local_record.toString(), newVars.defaultFields.resolved, quickServiceConfig.server_can_resolve, qs_notes + modifiedFields)
                if (incidentUpdate.status != 'processed') throw 'Incident not updated' + incidentUpdate.error;;
                processing_results += "\nIncident Updated: " + qs_relRec.local_record.number;
                try {
                    qs_relRec.update();
                    processing_results += "\nRelationship Updated: " + qs_relRec.quick_service_record;
                } catch (err) {
                    current.error = 'Quick Service inbound Related Record update failed:' + err;
                    current.status = 'error';
                }
            } catch (err) {
                current.error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed:' + err;
                current.status = 'error';
            }

        } else {
            current.error = 'GlideRecord query returned no task';
            current.status = 'error';
        }
    } catch (err) {
        current.error = 'GlideRecord query failure: ' + err;
        current.status = 'error';
    } finally {
        if (current.status == 'error') {
            this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "inbound_incident", localTask.sys_id, current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
        }
        current.retry_count = retryCount + 1;
        current.result = processing_results;
        current.update();
    }
};

quick_service_utils.updateIncident = function(incident_sysID, newvars_resolved, server_can_resolve, work_notes, processIdentifier) {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var incident = new GlideRecord('incident');
    incident.get(incident_sysID);
    var processing_results = "";
    var error = "";
    var status = "error";
    var logLevel = "Info";
    var phaseOfProcess = "quick_service_utils.updateIncident"
    if (processIdentifier)
        phaseOfProcess += ": " + processIdentifier;
    var testResults = {
        "status": "Passed",
        "incident_sysID": incident_sysID.toString(),
        "incident_number": incident.number.toString(),
        "newvars_resolved": newvars_resolved.toString(),
        "server_can_resolve": server_can_resolve.toString(),
        "results": ["Test Started at " + new GlideDateTime()]
    };
    incident[quickServiceConfig.incident_comments_field.element] = work_notes;
    testResults.incidentResolved = this.incidentResolved(incident.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
    if (newvars_resolved && server_can_resolve) {
        testResults.results.push("Passed permission requirments to resolve.");
        if (!this.incidentResolved(incident.state.getDisplayValue().toString())) {
            testResults.results.push("Passed Incident state check. Incident is not already resolved.");
            incident.state = quickServiceConfig.incident_state_when_resolved.value;
            var vars = {
                'incident': incident
            };
            var evaluator = new GlideScopedEvaluator();
            try {
                quickServiceConfig.resolution_script += "\ninc_answer = incident;";
                var inc_answer = evaluator.evaluateScript(quickServiceConfig, 'resolution_script', vars) ;
                if (inc_answer == null) throw 'Script not evaluated. Check system logs for more details.';
            } catch (err) {
                testResults.results.push("Failed to evaluate Resolution Script. Check system logs for more details.");
                testResults.status = 'Failed';
                logLevel = "Error";
            }

            var newOutbound = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
            newOutbound.initialize();
            newOutbound.type = 'outbound';
            newOutbound.action = 'update';
            newOutbound.status = 'ready';
            newOutbound.local_task = incident_sysID;
            newOutbound.task_type = "incident";
            newOutbound.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(incident);
            newOutbound.insert();
        } else {

            testResults.results.push("Incident already resolved.");
        }
    }
    if (testResults.status != 'Failed') {
        try {
            testResults.results.push("Updating Incident: " + incident.number);
            if (incident.update() == null) throw 'Incident not updated. Check system logs for more details.';
            processing_results += "\nIncident Updated: " + incident.number;
            status = "processed";

        } catch (err) {
            error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed:' + err;
            status = 'error';
            testResults.results.push("Incident update failed: " + err);
            testResults.status = 'Failed';
            logLevel = "Error";
        }
    } else {
        error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed.';
        status = 'error';
    }
    this.processErrors(logLevel, status, phaseOfProcess, incident_sysID, global.JSON.stringify(testResults));
    return {
        'processing_results': processing_results,
        'error': error,
        'status': status,
        'testResults': testResults
    };
};

            };
        }

quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum = function(attachment_b64) {

    var str = attachment_b64
    var hash = 0;
    if (str.length == 0) return hash;
    for (i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
        char2 = str.charCodeAt(i);
        hash = ((hash<<5)-hash)+char2;
        hash = hash & hash; // Convert to 32bit integer
    }
    return hash;
};

quick_service_utils.mapAttachment = function(attachment_gr){
        gs.info('mapAttachment: start')
    var checksumRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
    if(!checksumRec.get('attachment',attachment_gr.sys_id)){
        gs.info('mapAttachment: Mapping')

        var task_sysID = attachment_gr.table_sys_id;
        var table = attachment_gr.table_name;
        var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
        attachmentTable.get('name',table);
        var table_sysID = attachmentTable.sys_id;

        //Convert Attachment to b64
        var base64string = quick_service_utils.getBase64(attachment_gr.sys_id);

        // Check checksum
        var md5Hash = quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum(base64string)

        var uniquID = (attachment_gr.file_name + ":" + attachment_gr.content_type+":"+attachment_gr.table_name + ":" + attachment_gr.table_sys_id).substring(0,32)
        gs.info('mapAttachment: '+uniquID)
        var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
        checksumRecs.addEncodedQuery('task=' + task_sysID + '^table=' + table_sysID + '^attachment='+uniquID);
        checksumRecs.query();
        if (checksumRecs.next()) {
            checksumRecs.attachment=attachment_gr.sys_id;
            checksumRecs.update();
        }
    } else {
        gs.info('mapAttachment: already mapped')
    }
}

quick_service_utils.outboundAddAttachment = function(attachment_gr) {
    // variables
    var task_sysID = attachment_gr.table_sys_id;
    var table = attachment_gr.table_name;
    var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
    attachmentTable.get('name',table);
    var table_sysID = attachmentTable.sys_id;
    var customer = '';
    var task_type = "";
    var task_gr = new GlideRecord(table);
    task_gr.get(task_sysID);
    try {
        var relRec_gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
        relRec_gr.addEncodedQuery('local_record=' + task_sysID + '^active=true');
        relRec_gr.query();
    } catch (err) {}
    //Has active RelRec OR qs_task
    if (table == 'x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task' || relRec_gr.hasNext()) {
        relRec_gr.next();

        //Convert Attachment to b64
        var base64string = quick_service_utils.getBase64(attachment_gr.sys_id);

        // Check checksum
        var md5Hash = quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum(base64string)

        var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
        checksumRecs.addEncodedQuery('task=' + task_sysID + '^table=' + table_sysID + '^md5_hash=' + md5Hash + '^attachment='+attachment_gr.sys_id+'^ORattachment=pendingECC');
        checksumRecs.query();
        if (!checksumRecs.hasNext()) {
            var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
            quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
            customer = quickServiceConfig.sys_id;

            //Create checksum
            var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
            checksumRecs.initialize();
            checksumRecs.task = task_sysID;
            checksumRecs.table = table_sysID;
            checksumRecs.md5_hash = md5Hash;
            checksumRecs.attachment = attachment_gr.sys_id;
            checksumRecs.insert()

            //Create Outbund record     
            var theseParams = {
                "attachment":checksumRecs.remote_attachment.toString(),
                "remoteAttachment":attachment_gr.sys_id.toString(),
                "name": attachment_gr.file_name.toString(),
                "type": attachment_gr.content_type.toString(),
                "base64": base64string
            };

            var outbound = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
            outbound.initialize();
            outbound.type = 'outbound';
            outbound.action = 'add_attachment';
            outbound.status = 'ready';
            outbound.local_task = task_sysID;
            outbound.task_parameters = JSON.stringify(theseParams);
            if (table == "x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task")
                outbound.task_type = "qs task";
            else 
                outbound.task_type = table;
            outbound.insert();

            gs.info('base64string: '+base64string.length);
        } else {
            gs.info('Checksum already exists')
        }
    }
};

quick_service_utils.inboundAddAttatchment = function(inbound_object) {

    var retryCount = inbound_object.retry_count;
    inbound_object.u_status = 'Processing';
    inbound_object.update();
    inbound_object.status = 'processed';
    if(this.receiveAttachments()){
        try{
            var clientRec = global.JSON.parse(inbound_object.quick_service_task.toString());
            var payload = global.JSON.parse(inbound_object.payload);
            var serverTask = inbound_object.local_task;
            var table = inbound_object.local_task.sys_class_name;
            var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
            attachmentTable.get('name',table);
            var table_sysID = attachmentTable.sys_id;
    
            // check if attachment already exists
            gs.info('payload.base64: '+payload.base64)
            var md5Hash = quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum(payload.base64)
    
            var task_gr = new GlideRecord(table);
            task_gr.get(serverTask);

            // Istanbul and later releases
            var gsa = new GlideSysAttachment()
            var attachmentId = gsa.writeBase64(task_gr, payload.name,payload.type, payload.base64);   
    
            var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
            checksumRecs.initialize();
            checksumRecs.task = serverTask;
            checksumRecs.table = table_sysID;
            checksumRecs.md5_hash = md5Hash;
            checksumRecs.attachment = attachmentId;
            checksumRecs.remote_attachment = payload.remoteAttachment;
            var checksumRec = checksumRecs.insert();
            inbound_object.result = 'Checksum: ' + checksumRec;
    
        } catch(err){
            inbound_object.error = err;
            inbound_object.status = 'error';
        }
    } else {
        inbound_object.result = 'Inbound Attachments disabled: '
    }
    inbound_object.retry_count = retryCount + 1;
    inbound_object.update();
};

quick_service_utils.inboundDeleteAttatchment = function(inbound_object) {
    inbound_object.u_status = 'Processing';
    inbound_object.update();
    inbound_object.status = 'processed';
    if(this.receiveAttachments()){
        try{
            var clientRec = global.JSON.parse(inbound_object.quick_service_task.toString());
            var payload = global.JSON.parse(inbound_object.payload.toString());
            var serverTask = inbound_object.local_task;
            var table = inbound_object.local_task.sys_class_name;
            var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
            attachmentTable.get('name',table);
            var table_sysID = attachmentTable.sys_id;

            // check if attachment already exists
            var md5Hash = quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum(payload.base64)
        gs.info('task='+serverTask+'^table='+table_sysID+'^remote_attachment='+payload.remoteAttachment+'^ORattachment='+payload.attachment)
            var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');
                checksumRecs.addEncodedQuery('task='+serverTask+'^table='+table_sysID+'^remote_attachment='+payload.remoteAttachment+'^ORattachment='+payload.attachment);
                checksumRecs.query();
            if(checksumRecs.next()){
            
                var attachment = new GlideRecord('sys_attachment');
                attachment.query('sys_id',checksumRecs.attachment.sys_id)
                if(attachment.next()){
                    try{
                        var gsa = new GlideSysAttachment();
                        gsa.deleteAttachment(attachment.sys_id);
                        checksumRecs.deleteRecord();
                        inbound_object.result = 'Attachment '+attachment.file_name+' deleted.';
                    }catch (err){
                        inbound_object.error = 'Error on deleteRecord: '+err;
                        inbound_object.status = 'error';
                    }
                } else {
                    inbound_object.result = 'Attachment not found.';
                }
            } else {
                inbound_object.result = 'Checksum not found.';
            }
        }catch(err){
            inbound_object.error = 'Not able to delete attachment: '+err;
            inbound_object.status = 'error';
        }
    } else {
        inbound_object.result = 'Inbound Attachments disabled: '
    }
    inbound_object.retry_count = inbound_object.u_retry_count + 1;
    inbound_object.update();
};

quick_service_utils.outboundDeleteAttachment = function(attachment_gr) {
    // variables
    var task_sysID = attachment_gr.table_sys_id;
    var table = attachment_gr.table_name;
    var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
    attachmentTable.get('name',table);
    var table_sysID = attachmentTable.sys_id;

    task_gr.get(task_sysID);
    try {
        var relRec_gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
        relRec_gr.addEncodedQuery('local_record=' + task_sysID + '^active=true');
        relRec_gr.query();
    } catch (err) {}
    //Has active RelRec OR qs_task
    if (table == 'x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task' || relRec_gr.hasNext()) {
        relRec_gr.next();

        //Convert Attachment to b64
        var base64string = quick_service_utils.getBase64(attachment_gr.sys_id);

        //    var md5Hash = quick_service_utils.getMD5hash(base64string)
        var checksumRecs = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_attachment_checksums');

        checksumRecs.addEncodedQuery('attachment=' + attachment_gr.sys_id);
        checksumRecs.query();
        if (checksumRecs.next()) {

            //Create Outbund record

            quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);

            var theseParams = {
                "attachment":checksumRecs.remote_attachment.toString(),
                "remoteAttachment":attachment_gr.sys_id.toString(),

                "type": attachment_gr.content_type.toString(),
                "base64": base64string
            };

            var outbound = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
            outbound.initialize();
            outbound.type = 'outbound';
            outbound.action = 'delete_attachment';
            outbound.status = 'ready';
            outbound.local_task = task_sysID;
            outbound.task_parameters = JSON.stringify(theseParams);
            if (table == "x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task")
                outbound.task_type = "qs task";
            else 
                outbound.task_type = table;
            outbound.insert();

            //Delete checksum
            checksumRecs.deleteRecord();

            gs.info(base64string);
        } else {
            gs.info('Checksum does not exist')
        }
    }
};

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><name>QS - Process Inbound Attachment</name><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period>1970-01-01 00:00:05</run_period><run_start>2018-08-17 03:16:46</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 05:00:00</run_time><run_type>periodically</run_type><script><![CDATA[var inbounds = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound');
inbounds.addEncodedQuery('action=add_attachment^status=ready^NQaction=add_attachment^status=error^retry_count<6');
inbounds.orderByDesc('sys_created_on');
inbounds.query();
while (inbounds.next()) {
	gs.info("there is one attachment inbound update to be processed");
 if (inbounds.status == 'ready' ||inbounds.status == 'error')
	 quick_service_utils.inboundAddAttatchment(inbounds);
	 
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-17 04:10:00</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>0cc08b1cdb486b001cad0f95ca961998</sys_id><sys_mod_count>12</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process Inbound Attachment</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_0cc08b1cdb486b001cad0f95ca961998</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-09 12:20:41</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

inbnd_attchmnt.addEncodedQuery("action=delete_attachment^status=ready"+
						   "^NQaction=delete_attachment^status=error^retry_count<6");
inbnd_attchmnt.orderByDesc('sys_created_on');
inbnd_attchmnt.query();
while (inbnd_attchmnt.next()) {
 if (inbnd_attchmnt.status == 'ready' ||inbnd_attchmnt.status == 'error'  )
	 quick_service_utils.inboundDeleteAttatchment(inbnd_attchmnt);
	 
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-27 17:49:21</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e367697bdb4ceb002e2f28f3ca9619e8</sys_id><sys_mod_count>6</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process inbound Delete Attachments</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_e367697bdb4ceb002e2f28f3ca9619e8</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-09 12:20:43</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><name>QS - Process Inbound</name><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period>1970-01-01 00:00:05</run_period><run_start>2017-07-12 15:07:52</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 08:00:00</run_time><run_type>periodically</run_type><script><![CDATA[var inbounds = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound');
inbounds.addEncodedQuery('status=ready^NQstatus=error^retry_count<6');
inbounds.query();
while(inbounds.next()){
	var current = inbounds;
	
	if (inbounds.action == 'add_attachment')
		quick_service_utils.inboundAddAttatchment(inbounds);
	else if (inbounds.action == 'delete_attachment')
		quick_service_utils.inboundDeleteAttatchment(inbounds);
	else if (inbounds.task_type == 'incident')
		quick_service_utils.inbound_incident();
	else if (inbounds.task_type == 'qs task')
		quick_service_utils.inbound_qsTask();
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>cloudpires</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-07-12 15:09:39</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>befd5027dbbbb60010707ab9bf961964</sys_id><sys_mod_count>14</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process Inbound</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_befd5027dbbbb60010707ab9bf961964</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-09-17 20:53:50</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_matsa_quick_serv.quick_service_relatedrec</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>quick_service_relatedrec</name><script><![CDATA[var quick_service_relatedrec = Class.create();
quick_service_relatedrec.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
checkRelatedRecord : function() {
	
	var id=this.getParameter("sysparm_id");
	gs.info("incident id = "+id);
	var totalRelRecs=0;
	var i=0
	var secRecord="";
	var relationship = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
	if(relationship.get("local_record",id)){
		var num=relationship.number;
		if(num!=""){
			var secRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
		secRec.addQuery('number',num);
		secRec.orderByDesc('sys_created_on');
		//secRec.addAggregate('COUNT');
		secRec.query();
		while(secRec.next()){
			totalRelRecs=totalRelRecs+1;
			secRecord=secRec.local_record.number;
		}
		
		gs.info("total related records = "+totalRelRecs);
	return totalRelRecs+";"+secRecord;
		}
		
	}
},
checkParentscIncident : function() {
	
	var id=this.getParameter("sysparm_id");
	gs.info("incident id = "+id);
	var relationship = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
	relationship.get("resolved_incident",id)
		
		
			return relationship.local_record.number;
		
		
	
},
type: 'quick_service_relatedrec'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-09-21 18:17:00</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>bbcdd6f7db60e30044bc28f3ca9619cd</sys_id><sys_mod_count>12</sys_mod_count><sys_name>quick_service_relatedrec</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_bbcdd6f7db60e30044bc28f3ca9619cd</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-09-27 20:30:42</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><name>QS - Process inbound Incident Updates</name><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period>1970-01-01 00:00:05</run_period><run_start>2018-08-16 02:07:20</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 05:00:00</run_time><run_type>periodically</run_type><script><![CDATA[var inbnd_inc_upd = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound');
inbnd_inc_upd.addEncodedQuery("task_type=incident^action=update^status=ready"+
						   "^NQtask_type=incident^action=update^status=error^retry_count<6");
inbnd_inc_upd.orderByDesc('sys_created_on');
inbnd_inc_upd.query();
while (inbnd_inc_upd.next()) {
	gs.info("there is one inbound update to be processed");
 if (inbnd_inc_upd.status == 'ready' ||inbnd_inc_upd.status == 'error'  )
	 quick_service_utils.inbound_incident_update(inbnd_inc_upd);
	 
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-16 02:08:38</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>0547ed44db8c2b001cad0f95ca9619a0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process inbound Incident Updates</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_0547ed44db8c2b001cad0f95ca9619a0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-09 12:21:02</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

quick_service_utils.incidentUpdated = function(current, previous) {

    var fieldArr = quick_service_utils.getFields();
    var fieldsUpdated = false;

    for (var index in fieldArr) {
        if (current[fieldArr[index]] != previous[fieldArr[index]].toString()) {
            fieldsUpdated = true;
        }
    }
	
    return fieldsUpdated;

};

quick_service_utils.getFields = function() {

    var fieldsToMap = ['state'];

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);

    var incidentFields = new GlideRecord('sys_dictionary');
    incidentFields.addEncodedQuery("sys_idIN" + quickServiceConfig.qs_incidents_fields);
    incidentFields.query();
    while (incidentFields.next()) {
        if(fieldsToMap.indexOf(incidentFields.element.toString())<0)
            fieldsToMap.push(incidentFields.element.toString());
    }
	
    return fieldsToMap;
};

quick_service_utils.qsTaskUpdated = function(current, previous) {

    var fieldArr = quick_service_utils.getQsTaskFields(current.sys_id);
    var fieldsUpdated = false;
    for (var index in fieldArr) {

        if ((typeof(current[fieldArr[index]]) !== 'undefined') && (current[fieldArr[index]] != previous[fieldArr[index]])) {
            fieldsUpdated = true;
        }
    }
	
    return fieldsUpdated;

};

quick_service_utils.getQsTaskFields = function(sysID) {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var fieldsToMap = ["state","assigned_to","assignment_group","quick_service_customer_comments"];
    //fieldsToMap.push(quickServiceConfig)

    return fieldsToMap;
};

quick_service_utils.incidentResolved = function(incident_state) {
    var resolved = false;
    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var resolutionStates = quickServiceConfig.incident_resolved_state.getDisplayValue().split(',');

    for (var index in resolutionStates) {
        if (incident_state == resolutionStates[index].trim()) {
            resolved = true;
        }
    }
	
    return resolved;
};

quick_service_utils.syncTask = function(override, parameters) {
    // Create Outbound request

    if(quick_service_utils.quickServiceActive()){
		
        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
        gr.initialize();
        gr.type = 'outbound';
        //gr.action = current.operation();
        if (override == 'insert')
            gr.action = override;
		else{
			gr.action = override;
		}
        gr.status = 'ready';
        gr.local_task = current.getUniqueValue();
       // gr.customer = 'the customer';
        if (override == "qsIncidentCreate") {
            gr.task_type = "incident";
            gr.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(current); //parameters;

        } else if (current.sys_class_name.toString() == "x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task") {
			
            gr.task_type = "qs task";
            gr.task_parameters = current.quick_service_customer_comments;

        } else if (current.sys_class_name.toString() == "incident") {
            gr.task_type = "incident";
            gr.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(current);

        }
        gr.insert();
		if(override=="insert" && current.sys_class_name.toString() == "incident"){
			
		   var relatedRecord = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
				relatedRecord.addQuery("local_record",current.getUniqueValue());
				relatedRecord.query();
				while(relatedRecord.next()){
					relatedRecord.all_fields=gr.task_parameters;
					relatedRecord.update();
				}	
		   }
    } else {
        gs.addErrorMessage('QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord')
        gs.info("QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord")
    }
    return;

};

quick_service_utils.outbound_request = function() {
    if(quick_service_utils.quickServiceActive()){
        if (current.status == 'ready') {
            var additionalValues;

            if (current.action == 'insert') {

                if (this.outbound_insert()) {
					
                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_insert();
                } else {
                    return;
                }
            } else if (current.action == 'update') {

                if (this.outbound_update()) {
                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_update();
                } else {
                    return;
                }
            } else if (current.action == 'delete_attachment' || current.action == 'add_attachment') {

                    additionalValues = quick_service_utils.outbound_update();
                } else {
                    return;
                }

                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
				};
                if(current.action.toString()=="insert" && current.task_type=="qs task"){
					
					quick_service_task_obj = {

                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
                };
				}else if(current.action.toString()=="update" && current.task_type=="qs task"){
					
					var gr=new GlideRecord("x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task");
					gr.get(current.local_task);
					
					var inbound_obj=new GlideRecord("x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound");
					if(inbound_obj.get("server_request",gr.request)){
						gs.info("there is inbound task"+inbound_obj.client_task)
						quick_service_task_obj =inbound_obj.client_task;
					}
					var outboundObj = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
					outboundObj.addEncodedQuery('action=insert^local_task='+current.local_task);
					outboundObj.query();
					while(outboundObj.next()){
						gs.info("there is outbound task"+outboundObj.client_task)
					quick_service_task_obj =outboundObj.client_task;
					}
						
						
						
					
				}
				
				else if(current.action.toString()=="update" && current.task_type=="incident"){

                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
                };
				}else if((current.action=="add_attachment" || current.action == 'delete_attachment') && current.task_type=="qs task" && current.attachment_task_type=="internal"){
					
					quick_service_task_obj = {
                    "number": current.local_task.number.toString(),
                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
                };
						quick_service_task_obj = JSON.stringify(quick_service_task_obj);
					}else if((current.action=="add_attachment" || current.action == 'delete_attachment') && current.task_type=="qs task" && current.attachment_task_type=="external"){
						
						var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_inbound');
						gr.get('server_request',current.local_task.request);

						//gs.info("inbound client task = "+gr.u_client_task);
						
					}		
				else{
					quick_service_task_obj = {
                    "number": current.local_task.number.toString(),
                    "sysID": current.local_task.toString(),
                    "shortDes": current.local_task.short_description.toString(),
                    "description": current.local_task.description.toString()
                };
					//payloadObj.u_client_task = JSON.stringify(quick_service_task_obj);
				}
                var type="";
                var payloadObj = {};
				gs.info("additonal value = "+additionalValues.toString());

//                   if(gr.get("local_record",current.local_task)){
// 					  //gr.initialize();
