// 					}
                   
//                 } catch (err) {}
                payloadObj.u_task_type = current.task_type.toString();
                var payloadString = JSON.stringify(payloadObj);

                var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
                request.setEndpoint('https://' + current.quick_service_host.quick_service_host + '/api/now/table/x_matsa_qck_server_qs_inbound');
                request.setHttpMethod('POST');
                request.setBasicAuth(user, password);
                request.setRequestHeader("Accept", "application/json");
                request.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
                request.setRequestBody(payloadString);

                var response = request.execute();
                var respBody = response.getBody();
                current.payload = payloadString;
                current.result = respBody;
				if(current.action.toString()=="insert"){
					current.client_task=JSON.stringify(quick_service_task_obj);
				}else{
					current.client_task=quick_service_task_obj;
				}
				//current.client_task=JSON.stringify(quick_service_task_obj);
                if (respBody.match(/^\{\"error\"/)) {
                    current.error = respBody;
                    current.status = 'error';
                } else {
                    current.status = 'processed';
                }
            } catch (err) {
                
                current.error = 'Error sending Webservice: ' + err;
                current.status = 'error';
            }

        if (current.status == 'error') {
            this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "outbound_request", current.local_task.toString(), current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
        }
            current.update();
        }
    } else {
        gs.info("QuickService ERROR: No active config reocord")
    }
};

quick_service_utils.outbound_insert = function() {
	
    var theseVars = false;
    if (current.task_type == 'qs task') {
		
        var varObj = {};
        try {
            var varRelationships = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_variables');
            varRelationships.addEncodedQuery('variable.active=true^catalog_item=' + current.local_task.request_item.cat_item.sys_id.toString());
            varRelationships.query();
            while (varRelationships.next()) {
				
                varObj[varRelationships.getUniqueValue()] = {
                    "variable_sysID": varRelationships.variable.sys_id.toString(),
                    "label": varRelationships.variable.question_text.toString(),
                    "name": varRelationships.variable.name.toString(),
                    "order": varRelationships.variable.order.toString(),
                    "display_value": '',
                    "value": ''
                };
            }

            var gr = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
            if (gr.get(current.local_task.request_item.toString())) {
                for (var index in varObj) {
                    
						if(typeof(gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID]) !== 'undefined'){
                        varObj[index].display_value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID].getDisplayValue();
                        varObj[index].value = gr.variables[varObj[index].variable_sysID.toString()].toString();
						}
                   
                }
            }
            theseVars = global.JSON.stringify(varObj);
        } catch (err) {
            current.error = 'Error fetching vars: ' + err;
            current.status = 'error';
            current.update();
        }
    } else if (current.task_type == 'incident') {
        theseVars = current.task_parameters;
        theseVars.state= current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.number= current.local_task.number.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.assigned_to= current.local_task.assigned_to.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.assignment_group= current.local_task.assignment_group.getDisplayValue().toString();
        theseVars.qs_task= current.qs_task_number;
        theseVars.resolved= quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
        theseVars.active= !quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
    }
    return theseVars;
};

quick_service_utils.outbound_update = function() {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var task_vars = false;
    if (current.task_type == 'qs task') {

        if(current.action == 'add_attachment' || current.action == 'delete_attachment')
            task_vars = global.JSON.parse(current.task_parameters);
        else
            task_vars = {};
        task_vars.state= current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString();
        task_vars.task_number= current.local_task.number.getDisplayValue().toString();
        task_vars.assigned_to= current.local_task.assigned_to.getDisplayValue().toString();
        task_vars.assignment_group= current.local_task.assignment_group.getDisplayValue().toString();
        task_vars.work_notes= current.local_task.work_notes.getJournalEntry(1);
        task_vars.updated_by= gs.getUser().getDisplayName();
        task_vars.qs_task= current.qs_task_number;


        if(quickServiceConfig.getValue('comments_by_qstask') == 'config_local_user')
            task_vars.updated_by = quickServiceConfig.getDisplayValue('local_user').toString();

    } else if (current.task_type == 'incident') {
        task_vars = global.JSON.parse(current.task_parameters);
         task_vars.state= current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString();
         task_vars.number= current.local_task.number.getDisplayValue().toString();
         task_vars.assigned_to= current.local_task.assigned_to.getDisplayValue().toString();
         task_vars.assignment_group= current.local_task.assignment_group.getDisplayValue().toString();
         task_vars.qs_task= current.qs_task_number;
         task_vars.resolved= quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
         task_vars.active= !quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(current.local_task.state.getDisplayValue().toString())
		 if(current.local_task.state.toString()=='6'){
	var myGR = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
	if (myGR.get('local_record',current.local_task)) {
		myGR.active=false;
		myGR.update();
	}
}
		 }
   
    return global.JSON.stringify(task_vars);
};

quick_service_utils.inbound_qsTask = function() {
    var varCount = 0;
    var localTask = current.local_task;
    var server_qs_task = global.JSON.parse(current.payload);
    try {
        var qs_task = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_task');
        if (qs_task.get(current.local_task.toString())) {

            qs_task.qs_state = server_qs_task.state;
            if (server_qs_task.state.match(/Closed Complete/)) { // && qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.resolution_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.resolution_state.value;
            } else if (server_qs_task.state.match(/Closed/)) { // && qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.cancelled_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.cancelled_state.value;
            } else if (qs_task.state != current.quick_service_host.open_state.value) {
                qs_task.state = current.quick_service_host.open_state.value;
                if (!qs_task.active) {
                    qs_task.active = true;
                }
            }
            qs_task.qs_task_number = server_qs_task.number;
            qs_task.qs_assigned_to = server_qs_task.assigned_to;
            qs_task.qs_assignment_group = server_qs_task.assignment_group;
            qs_task.qs_task_sysid = server_qs_task.sys_id;
            qs_task.expedited_request = server_qs_task.u_expedited_request;
            qs_task.quickservice_closed_by = server_qs_task.closed_by;
            qs_task.close_notes = server_qs_task.close_notes;
            if (server_qs_task.work_notes && !server_qs_task.work_notes.match(/\_123STREAMENTRY321\_/g)) {
                var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
                quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
                qs_task[quickServiceConfig.qs_comments_field.element] = server_qs_task.updated_by + ' commented: ' + server_qs_task.work_notes;
            }
            qs_task.update();

            current.result = 'Task updated:' + qs_task.number;
            current.status = 'processed';
        } else {
            current.error = 'GlideRecord query returned no task';
            current.status = 'error';
        }
    } catch (err) {
        current.error = 'GlideRecord query failure: ' + err;
        current.status = 'error';
    }

    if (current.status == 'error') {
        this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "inbound_qsTask", localTask.sys_id, current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
    }
    current.update();
};

quick_service_utils.inbound_incident = function() {
    var retryCount = current.retry_count;
    var processing_results = 'Processing Results';
    var updated = false;
    var varCount = 0;
    var localTask = current.local_task;
    var newVars = global.JSON.parse(current.payload);
    try {
        var qs_relRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
        qs_relRec.addQuery('active', true);
        qs_relRec.addQuery('local_record', current.local_task);
        qs_relRec.query();
        if (qs_relRec.next()) {
            var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
            quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
            qs_relRec.quick_service_record = newVars.defaultFields.number;
            qs_relRec.client_task_data = '{"number":"' + newVars.defaultFields.number + '","sys_Id":' + newVars.defaultFields.sys_id + '"}';
            // Check if resolved
            if (newVars.defaultFields.resolved && quickServiceConfig.server_can_resolve) {
                qs_relRec.active = false;
            }

            var qs_notes = "Quick Service Notes\n";
            for (var field in newVars.fieldsToMap) {

                if ((typeof(qs_relRec[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]]) !== 'undefined') && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue) {
                    qs_relRec[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]] = newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                }
                if (newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].type == 'journal_input' && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue && !newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.match(/\_123STREAMENTRY321\_/g)) {
                        qs_notes = newVars.defaultFields.updated_by.toString() + " commented: " + newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                }
                updated = true;
            }
            // Check for work notes

            var modifiedFields = "";
            if (qs_relRec.all_fields) {
                var oldVars = JSON.parse(qs_relRec.all_fields);
                var fieldsModified = false;
                for (var index in newVars.customFields) {
                    if (newVars.customFields[index].value.toString() != oldVars[index].value.toString() && newVars.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input") {
                        if (!fieldsModified) {
                            modifiedFields = "\nModified Fields:\n";
                            fieldsModified = true;
                        }
                        modifiedFields += newVars.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + newVars.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
                    }
                }
            } else {
                for (var index in newVars.customFields) {
                    if (newVars.customFields[index].value && newVars.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input") {
                        if (!fieldsModified) {
                            modifiedFields = "\nModified Fields:\n";
                            fieldsModified = true;
                        }
                        modifiedFields += newVars.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + newVars.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
                    }
                }
            }

            qs_relRec.work_notes = qs_notes + modifiedFields;

            qs_relRec.all_fields = JSON.stringify(newVars.customFields);


            current.status = 'processed';
            try {
                var incidentUpdate = this.updateIncident(qs_relRec.local_record.toString(), newVars.defaultFields.resolved, quickServiceConfig.server_can_resolve, qs_notes + modifiedFields)
                if (incidentUpdate.status != 'processed') throw 'Incident not updated' + incidentUpdate.error;;
                processing_results += "\nIncident Updated: " + qs_relRec.local_record.number;
                try {
                    qs_relRec.update();
                    processing_results += "\nRelationship Updated: " + qs_relRec.quick_service_record;
                } catch (err) {
                    current.error = 'Quick Service inbound Related Record update failed:' + err;
                    current.status = 'error';
                }
            } catch (err) {
                current.error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed:' + err;
                current.status = 'error';
            }

        } else {
            current.error = 'GlideRecord query returned no task';
            current.status = 'error';
        }
    } catch (err) {
        current.error = 'GlideRecord query failure: ' + err;
        current.status = 'error';
    } finally {
        if (current.status == 'error') {
            this.processErrors("Error", "Error", "inbound_incident", localTask.sys_id, current.error, current.sys_id.toString());
        }
        current.retry_count = retryCount + 1;
        current.result = processing_results;
        current.update();
    }
};

quick_service_utils.updateIncident = function(incident_sysID, newvars_resolved, server_can_resolve, work_notes, processIdentifier) {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var incident = new GlideRecord('incident');
    incident.get(incident_sysID);
    var processing_results = "";
    var error = "";
    var status = "error";
    var logLevel = "Info";
    var phaseOfProcess = "quick_service_utils.updateIncident"
    if (processIdentifier)
        phaseOfProcess += ": " + processIdentifier;
    var testResults = {
        "status": "Passed",
        "incident_sysID": incident_sysID.toString(),
        "incident_number": incident.number.toString(),
        "newvars_resolved": newvars_resolved.toString(),
        "server_can_resolve": server_can_resolve.toString(),
        "results": ["Test Started at " + new GlideDateTime()]
    };
    incident[quickServiceConfig.incident_comments_field.element] = work_notes;
    testResults.incidentResolved = this.incidentResolved(incident.state.getDisplayValue().toString());
    if (newvars_resolved && server_can_resolve) {
        testResults.results.push("Passed permission requirments to resolve.");
        if (!this.incidentResolved(incident.state.getDisplayValue().toString())) {
            testResults.results.push("Passed Incident state check. Incident is not already resolved.");
            incident.state = quickServiceConfig.incident_state_when_resolved.value;
            var vars = {
                'incident': incident
            };
            var evaluator = new GlideScopedEvaluator();
            try {
                quickServiceConfig.resolution_script += "\ninc_answer = incident;";
                var inc_answer = evaluator.evaluateScript(quickServiceConfig, 'resolution_script', vars) ;
                if (inc_answer == null) throw 'Script not evaluated. Check system logs for more details.';
            } catch (err) {
                testResults.results.push("Failed to evaluate Resolution Script. Check system logs for more details.");
                testResults.status = 'Failed';
                logLevel = "Error";
            }

            var newOutbound = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_outbound');
            newOutbound.initialize();
            newOutbound.type = 'outbound';
            newOutbound.action = 'update';
            newOutbound.status = 'ready';
            newOutbound.local_task = incident_sysID;
            newOutbound.task_type = "incident";
            newOutbound.task_parameters = quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams(incident);
            newOutbound.insert();
        } else {

            testResults.results.push("Incident already resolved.");
        }
    }
    if (testResults.status != 'Failed') {
        try {
            testResults.results.push("Updating Incident: " + incident.number);
            if (incident.update() == null) throw 'Incident not updated. Check system logs for more details.';
            processing_results += "\nIncident Updated: " + incident.number;
            status = "processed";

        } catch (err) {
            error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed:' + err;
            status = 'error';
            testResults.results.push("Incident update failed: " + err);
            testResults.status = 'Failed';
            logLevel = "Error";
        }
    } else {
        error = 'Quick Service inbound Incident update failed.';
        status = 'error';
    }
    this.processErrors(logLevel, status, phaseOfProcess, incident_sysID, global.JSON.stringify(testResults));
    return {
        'processing_results': processing_results,
        'error': error,
        'status': status,
        'testResults': testResults
    };
};

quick_service_utils.getIncidentParams = function(incident) {

    var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
    quickServiceConfig.get('active', true);
    var fieldsToMap = quick_service_utils.getFields();
    var fieldObj = {
        'fieldsToMap': fieldsToMap,
        'customFields': {},
        'defaultFields':{
            'priority':incident.priority.toString(),
            'shortDes':incident.short_description.toString(),
            'description':incident.description.toString(),
            'number':incident.number.toString(),
            'updated_by':gs.getUser().getDisplayName().toString()
        } 
    };

    if(quickServiceConfig.getValue('comment_as_incident') == 'config_local_user')
        fieldObj.defaultFields.updated_by = quickServiceConfig.getDisplayValue('local_user').toString();

    for (var index in fieldsToMap) {
        var fieldType = incident.getElement(fieldsToMap[index]).getED().getInternalType();
        var fieldLabel = incident.getElement(fieldsToMap[index]).getLabel();
        if (fieldType == 'journal_input') {
            fieldObj.customFields[fieldsToMap[index]] = {
                'displayValue': '',
                'value': '',
                'type': fieldType,
                'label': fieldLabel
            };
            if (gs.getUserID() != quickServiceConfig.local_user.sys_id.toString()) {
                fieldObj.customFields[fieldsToMap[index]].displayValue = incident[fieldsToMap[index]].toString();
                fieldObj.customFields[fieldsToMap[index]].value = incident[fieldsToMap[index]].toString();
            }
        } else {
            fieldObj.customFields[fieldsToMap[index]] = {
                'displayValue': incident.getDisplayValue(fieldsToMap[index].toString()),
                'value': incident[fieldsToMap[index]].toString(),
                'type': fieldType,
                'label': fieldLabel
            };
        }
    }
    var vars = {
        'incident':incident
    };
    var evaluator = new GlideScopedEvaluator();
    evaluator.evaluateScript(quickServiceConfig, 'custom_fields',vars);
    try {
        for (var ex_index in extendedFields) {
            fieldObj.customFields[ex_index] = {};
            fieldObj.customFields[ex_index].value = extendedFields[ex_index].toString();
            fieldObj.customFields[ex_index].label = ex_index;
            try {
                fieldObj.customFields[ex_index].displayValue = extendedFields[ex_index].getDisplayValue().toString();
            } catch (err) {
                fieldObj.customFields[ex_index].displayValue = extendedFields[ex_index].toString();
            }
        }
    } catch (err) {}
    return global.JSON.stringify(fieldObj);
};

quick_service_utils.getMD5checksum = function(attachment_b64) {

    var str = attachment_b64
    var hash = 0;
    if (str.length == 0) return hash;
    for (i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
        char2 = str.charCodeAt(i);
        hash = ((hash<<5)-hash)+char2;
        hash = hash & hash; // Convert to 32bit integer
    }
    return hash;
};

        var attachmentTable = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
        attachmentTable.get('name',table);

//called by the scheduled script "QS - Process Inbound Incident Inserts" when an inbound record(task/incident) is inserted
quick_service_utils.inbound_incident_insert = function(inbound_object) { //inbound_object is qs_inbound table record object
    var retryCount = inbound_object.retry_count;
    inbound_object.retry_count = retryCount + 1;

    inbound_object.status = 'Processing';
    inbound_object.update();
//     var startTime = new GlideDateTime();
//     var results = "Processing start: " + startTime + "\n";
//     var error;

    var local_qs_incident = createIncident();
	
	inbound_object.local_task = local_qs_incident;
	inbound_object.update();
    //results += "Created Incident: " + new GlideDateTime() + "\n sys_id: " + local_qs_incident + "\n";

    var relationship = createRelationship();
    //results += "Created relationship." + new GlideDateTime() + "\n";


//     var endTime = new GlideDateTime();
//     results += "Processing end: " + endTime;
    
    inbound_object.status = 'processed';
    //inbound_object.result = results;
	//var user=gs.getUser();
	//inbound_object.u_caller= inbound_object.u_customer.u_local_user;
    inbound_object.update();


    function createRelationship() {
        var clientRec = JSON.parse(inbound_object.client_task);
        var newVars = JSON.parse(inbound_object.payload);

        var relationship = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_related_record');
        relationship.initialize();

        for (var field in newVars.fieldsToMap) {
            if ((typeof(relationship['u_' + newVars.fieldsToMap[field]]) !== 'undefined') && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]]) {
                relationship['u_' + newVars.fieldsToMap[field]] = newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue;
            }
        }
        relationship.active = true;
        relationship.quick_service_task = inbound_object.client_task;
        relationship.local_record = local_qs_incident;
       // relationship.u_caller = inbound_object.u_caller;
        //relationship.preferred_contact_method = newVars.defaultFields.preferred_method_of_contact;
//         relationship.u_assigned_to_business_phone = newVars.defaultFields.assigned_to_business_phone;
//         relationship.u_assigned_to_mobile_phone = newVars.defaultFields.assigned_to_mobile_phone;
//         relationship.u_assigned_to_email = newVars.defaultFields.assigned_to_email;
        relationship.number = newVars.defaultFields.number;
        relationship.priority = newVars.defaultFields.priority;
        relationship.short_description = newVars.defaultFields.shortDes;
        relationship.description = newVars.defaultFields.description;
		relationship.customer=inbound_object.customer;
		relationship.caller=inbound_object.customer.u_local_user;
        relationship.quick_service_customer_comments = newVars.defaultFields.comments + "\nVariables from client: " + JSON.stringify(newVars, null, 2);
        relationship.fieldstomap = JSON.stringify(newVars.fieldsToMap);
        relationship.all_fields = JSON.stringify(newVars);
		relationship.type="external";
        var newRelationship = relationship.insert();

        quick_service_utils_client.sync_incident(local_qs_incident);
        return newRelationship.u_number;
    }

    function createIncident() {

        var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
        quickServiceConfig.get(inbound_object.customer.sys_id); //u_customer is the config record
		
  //      var templateObj = JSON.parse('{"' + inbound_object.u_customer.u_template.replace("^EQ", '"').replace(/\=/g, '":"').replace(/\^/g, '","').toString() + '}');
        var inbound_payload = JSON.parse(inbound_object.payload);
        var custComments = '';
        var modifiedFields = "Quick Service Fields:\n";
        for (var index in inbound_payload.customFields) {
            if (inbound_payload.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input" && inbound_payload.customFields[index].displayValue) {
                modifiedFields += inbound_payload.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + inbound_payload.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
            } else if (inbound_payload.customFields[index].type.toString() == "journal_input" && inbound_payload.customFields[index].displayValue) {
                custComments = '\n' + inbound_payload.defaultFields.updated_by.toString() + " commented: " + inbound_payload.customFields[index].displayValue;
            }
        }
        var incident = new GlideRecord('incident');
        incident.initialize();
        incident.short_description = 'Quick Service Incident: ' + inbound_object.customer.getDisplayValue();
        incident.description = inbound_payload.defaultFields.shortDes + "\n" + inbound_payload.defaultFields.description;
        incident.work_notes = modifiedFields + custComments;
        incident.caller_id = quickServiceConfig.u_local_user; //gs.getUserID();
        incident.opened_by = quickServiceConfig.u_local_user; //gs.getUserID();
//         incident.impact = 2;
//         incident.urgency = 3;
		incident.priority=inbound_payload.defaultFields.priority;
	
        incident.sys_created_by = inbound_object.sys_created_by;
        incident.state = 1;
   //   for (var tempIndex in templateObj) {
   //       incident[tempIndex] = templateObj[tempIndex];
   //   }

        try {
            var incidentVars = { 
                'incident': incident,
                'inbound_payload':global.JSON.stringify(inbound_payload)
             };
            var evaluator = new GlideScopedEvaluator();
            evaluator.evaluateScript(quickServiceConfig, 'u_on_insert_script_incident', incidentVars);
        } catch (err) {
            gs.debug('Quick Service: createIncident evaluateScript error: '+err)
        }

        var newInc = incident.insert();
        return newInc;
    }
};

            incident.get(inbound_object.local_task);
            var quickServiceConfig = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_quick_serv_qs_customer');
            quickServiceConfig.get("active",true);
			
            if ((newVars.resolved || newVars.state=="Resolved") && quickServiceConfig.server_can_resolve) {
				gs.info("state is resolved");
                relationship.active = false;
// 				var inc=new GlideRecord("incident");
// 				inc.initialize();
// 				inc.caller_id=incident.caller_id;
// 				inc.assignment_group=incident.assignment_group;
// 				inc.short_description=incident.short_description;
// // 				inc.u_quick_service=true;
// // 				inc.u_quick_service_rec=incident.sys_id;
// 				var inc_id=inc.insert();
// 				relationship.resolved_incident=inc_id;
              //gs.log('incidentResolved: ' + !quick_service_utils_client.incidentResolved(inbound_object.u_customer, relationship.u_task))
                if (!quick_service_utils.incidentResolved(quickServiceConfig.sys_id, relationship.local_record)) {
					
                    incident.state = quickServiceConfig.incident_state_when_resolved.value;
                    var vars = {
                        'incident': incident
                    };
                    var evaluator = new GlideScopedEvaluator();
                    evaluator.evaluateScript(quickServiceConfig, 'resolution_script', vars);
                }
            }
            var qs_notes = "Quick Service Notes\n";
            for (var field in newVars.fieldsToMap) {
			gs.info("there are fields to map");
                if ((typeof(relationship[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]]) !== 'undefined') && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue) {
					
                    relationship[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]] = newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                }
                if (newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].type == 'journal_input' && newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue && !newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.match(/\_123STREAMENTRY321\_/g)) {
                    qs_notes = newVars.defaultFields.updated_by.toString() + " commented: " + newVars.customFields[newVars.fieldsToMap[field]].displayValue.toString();
                    addNotes = true;
                }
                updated = true;
            }

            // Check for worknotes
            var fieldsModified = false;
            var modifiedFields = "";
			try{
            for (var index in newVars.customFields) {
				
                if (newVars.customFields[index].value.toString() != oldVars.customFields[index].value.toString() && newVars.customFields[index].type.toString() != "journal_input") {
					
                    if (!fieldsModified) {
						gs.info("fields have been modified");
                        modifiedFields = "\nModified Fields:\n";
                        fieldsModified = true;
                    }
                    modifiedFields += newVars.customFields[index].label.toString() + " : " + newVars.customFields[index].displayValue.toString() + "\n";
                    addNotes = true;
					gs.info("modified fields = " + modifiedFields+ "addnotes = "+addNotes+"type of addNotes "+typeof addNotes);
                }
            }
				} catch(err){
				gs.info("got an exception ="+err);
			}
		gs.info("just before the if block");
            if (addNotes) {
				gs.info("in the if block");
                incident.work_notes = qs_notes + modifiedFields;
                relationship.work_notes = qs_notes + modifiedFields;
                processingNotes = qs_notes + modifiedFields;
            } else {
					gs.info("no fields have been modified");			
                processingNotes = "No Fields Updated";
            }
            relationship.all_fields = JSON.stringify(newVars);
			relationship.number=oldVars.number;
            incident.update();
            var newRelationship = relationship.update();
            return {
                "updated": updated,
                "notes": processingNotes + "\n",
                "local_qs_incident": relationship.local_record
            };
        }
    }

};



]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>cloudpires</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-06-21 11:33:57</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>3d336720db633200e46473abbf9619db</sys_id><sys_mod_count>644</sys_mod_count><sys_name>quick_service_utils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_3d336720db633200e46473abbf9619db</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-17 03:19:22</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

						   "^NQtask_type=incident^action=insert^status=error^retry_count<6");

inbnd_tsk_upd.addEncodedQuery("status=ready^task_type=qs task^action=update"+
						   "^NQstatus=error^task_type=qs task^action=update^retry_count<6");
inbnd_tsk_upd.orderBy('sys_created_on');
inbnd_tsk_upd.query();
while (inbnd_tsk_upd.next()) {
 if (inbnd_tsk_upd.status == 'ready' ||inbnd_tsk_upd.status == 'error')
	 quick_service_utils.inbound_task_update(inbnd_tsk_upd);
	 
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>akanksha.gupta</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-14 21:13:15</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e32a1b6bdbb3d3002e2f28f3ca9619bb</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>QS - Process Inbound Task Update</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Quick Service" source="x_matsa_quick_serv">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Quick Service">eaee9bacdb233200e46473abbf9619fa</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_e32a1b6bdbb3d3002e2f28f3ca9619bb</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-09 12:20:39</sys_updated_on><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>
